cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object detection on grid maps generated from sensor data. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper focuses on automated driving scenarios. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes an adversarial training approach for domain adaptation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with developing a robust object detector. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with object detection on grid maps, which can be considered a form of multimedia data.
